          "type": "ai_gen_block_15e7c06",
          "name": "Title and text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What Is a Magnetic Gym Bag?",
            "text": "<p>A magnetic gym bag is a compact storage bag that is designed to be used in a gym setting. The bag has several magnets that can hold and stick to metal equipment in the gym, including squat racks, exercise benches, lockers, and exercise machines.<br\/>This way, the users of the gym can have their belongings with them at all times, without having to walk to their lockers every now and then.<br\/>A compact fitness gym bag, unlike other ordinary gym bags, keeps everything organized and out of the floor.<br\/><\/p>",
            "desktop_width_percent": 100,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "spacing": 15,
            "padding_top": 40,
            "padding_bottom": 40,
            "padding_horizontal": 20,
            "background_color": "#ffffff",
            "heading_color": "#12395e",
            "text_color": "#202025",
